## Including Plots

You can also embed plots, for example:

```{r pressure, echo=FALSE}
plot(pressure)
```

Note that the `echo = FALSE` parameter was added to the code chunk to prevent printing of the R code that generated the plot.

# Code Chunks for other programming languages 

You can also write code in othe programming languages, for example in python:
```{python, echo=FALSE}
my_list = [1,2,3,4]
```
 
Or in bash:
```{bash, echo=FALSE}
ls
```
